            (WebCore::sRGBColorSpaceRef): Deleted.
            * platform/graphics/cg/ImageBufferCG.cpp:
            (WebCore::ImageBuffer::putByteArray):
            * platform/graphics/cocoa/IOSurface.mm:
            (IOSurface::createFromImage):
